Help
When you mention this bot in a reply to a message, it generates an image from that message.
Available options:
(If you specify more than one, separate them with ,) - light/l : Makes the background of the image white - color/c : Color the user icon - flip/f : Flip the image - bold/b : Make the text bold - new/n : Use new type image generation - font=<Font name> : Change the font to the specified one. learn more
Command Example:
- @Make it a Quote : Normal Quote - @Make it a Quote light : Light Quote - @Make it a Quote b, f : bold and flip Quote - @Make it a Quote font=pop, c : Color avatar Quote (font: pop)
